{"tid":1005893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你哋有冇諗過點解啲人嚟香港可以講普通話 唔入鄉隨俗","createTime":"2019-02-02T14:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T16:51:15.000Z","uid":114281,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7b5247c638cf4fa5ccfa4d7ace701e45775878e3","tid":1005893,"uid":114281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"係因為佢哋好多都覺得唔識廣東話 唔緊要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講普通話你哋都識聽嘅</span><br />\n隔離有個post話小朋友講慣普通話 講廣東話唔習慣就唔講<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個小朋友去到日本 韓國 美國呢？<br />\n佢會生存唔到 佢一定要焗住講日文韓文英文<br />\n<br />\n佢哋好似攞正牌咁話唔識聽廣東話唔識講廣東話<br />\n你哋都可以拎正牌同佢講你唔識<br />\n<br />\n如果係有一刻想香港係好嘅 想第時唔要淨係講普通話嘅<br />\n<br />\n希望你哋俾多少少堅持 俾多少少任性<br />\n<br />\n淨係講廣東話  就算你識聽 就算要浪費多少少時間都好<br />\n<br />\n一句都唔好講 好唔扮識聽... 等佢哋明白講講東話嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尤其係連登仔你哋   第時候你哋有好多都會係僱主 都會係有影響力嘅人 所以希望你唔好屈服......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我真係唔想有種 第時係香港個個都講普通話 然後你焗住要講普通話果種屈辱感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"30119c83fb535da8b7827a3c1fdb210e20658cf2","tid":1005893,"uid":114281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf87719bb1db9f0c451fbcbc2999f3a19f3822c0","tid":1005893,"uid":136763,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"大陸人大部分都覺得老撚馮<br />\n而我地香港人習慣屈服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93edfbfa90a5682da0e6573d824cdc511dca819","tid":1005893,"uid":156812,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T15:19:05.000Z","msg":"唔駛扮<br />\n根本就唔識聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到講蝗語既學生會直接講大陸人/蝗蟲<br />\n不過佢哋好似聽到都唔覺得羞恥咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0ebd28f91f103151c5362c415f4b5b2c94a898","tid":1005893,"uid":81296,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T15:21:17.000Z","msg":"如果香港有一半人好似你咁諗就好<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"9e57d87186ce98521eddef3f1c738c9bad535189","tid":1005893,"uid":114281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T20:22:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbbad6db42fcd356ef19e78fd184453f6cf63a1","tid":1005893,"uid":79410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T20:24:43.000Z","msg":"其實啲支那人去外國一樣同人講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我就一定扮唔識"},{"pid":"972ab54b463422d20028100b54744d9b1785980b","tid":1005893,"uid":120821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T20:28:21.000Z","msg":"基本上係香港，如果有人講普通話即刻扮唔識聽，等佢講過，你黎香港點解我要就你？<br />\n就等於我去第二度都唔會講廣東話問嘢"},{"pid":"f3c08af5488eea27ec8f513a5788509327d0a0db","tid":1005893,"uid":217214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T21:55:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ca6da649c212a109fcdb1c8e2cc4a498dc5e6163","tid":1005893,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T21:58:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fe0bd1ebea57cb0e21483bee784e704582f530","tid":1005893,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T22:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834a515ad52867724c058c737948da1a5f094fb9","tid":1005893,"uid":126412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7b43f117a77bae5391687f0c67e135149315d2f","tid":1005893,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b5247c638cf4fa5ccfa4d7ace701e45775878e3","tid":1005893,"uid":114281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB